Austrians Want Hitler Back?

The Austrian newspaper Der Standard reported the surprising results of a survey in March 2013.

Fully 60 percent of Austrians want a “strong man” to run the country. Forty-two percent were willing to admit that, “Not everything was bad
under Hitler.”
